Evaluate Your Scheduling Efficiency with the Appointment Analytics App

Learn about your team’s appointment volume and your reps’ performance to see how well your service team is applying their resources to meet customer needs.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition. Requires a CRM Analytics license.
To create and manage the Appointment Analytics app: Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps
To use the Appointment Analytics app: Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps

Before creating an app, make sure you have at least two rows of data in the Service Appointment object and Lightning Scheduler is set up.

From the Analytics tab or Analytics Studio, click Create and then select App.
Select the Appointment Analytics template to open the guided flow.
Name and save your app.
title: Evaluating Scheduling Efficiency with Appointment Analytics
